A:  the dependency for poi is different version:

if your pom.xml contain both poi and testcase-annotation: the latter's poi version is 3.10, the first is 3.8. so popup the error.
		<dependency>
			<groupId>org.apache.poi</groupId>
			<artifactId>poi</artifactId>
			<version>3.8</version>
			<type>jar</type>
			<scope>compile</scope>
		</dependency>
